title: Scohoolgirl Apocalypse [2013 Japanese zombie movie]
description:
New 2013 Japanese zombie flick. 

Better than most the other shitty zombie flicks you've seen. 

IMDb: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt2360114/

8.4/10 from 12 users, on IMDb, as of 09/10/2013, so whatever that means.

Trailer: /watch?v=PqVBP6BHCLE

The video may skip a bit. I did the best I could with what I had. I did everything I could. For me, it works just fine.
